strings:
<voice_0x01001574><se_def>Marcello: What!? W-What are you doing!?
...Let me go!
<voice_0x01001575><se_def>Marcello: If you...hadn't interfered...I could have had all of Rhapthorne's power...
<voice_0x01001576><se_def>Marcello: But...it's all over now... All hope...is gone...
<voice_0x01001577><se_def>Marcello: Let me go! I don't want your help!
<voice_0x01001578><se_def>Angelo: No. I won't let you die.
<voice_0x01001579><se_def>Angelo: You will go on living, knowing that the brother you despised your whole life took pity on you.
<voice_0x0100157A><se_def>Angelo: I won't let you have everything your own way.
<voice_0x0100157B><se_def>Marcello: You're determined...to disgrace me more!? You...!

<voice_0x0100157D><se_def>Angelo: More than ten years. It was more than ten years ago that I first came to the abbey having lost
my family.
<voice_0x0100157E><se_def>Angelo: And you were the first person I spoke to.
<voice_0x0100157F><se_def>Angelo: I had nothing. No family, no home... I was all alone and I didn't know anyone at the abbey.
<voice_0x01001580><se_def>Angelo: You were kind to me. Just for those first few moments, you were genuinely kind.

<voice_0x01001581><se_def>Angelo: As soon as you found out who I was,
it changed everything...
<voice_0x01001582><se_def>Angelo: But, I never forgot that moment of kindness.
<voice_0x01001583><se_def>Marcello: You will regret the day you saved my life.
<voice_0x01001584><se_def>Angelo: You know, I really don't care. Do your worst. You can't hurt me any more.
<voice_0x01001586><se_def>Angelo: Isn't this your ring? Your Templar's ring?
<voice_0x01001587><se_def>Marcello: It's yours. It means nothing to me now.
<voice_0x01001588><se_high>Jessica: Angelo...

<voice_0x01001589><se_high>Jessica: Are you just going to let him leave?
He's really badly hurt.
